title: Exception is thrown during data export from a table containing highlight/map
description:
Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the attached report
2. Locate the table that contains highlight/map
3. Export the data from the table

OB: 

EB: The data from the table should be successfully exported

SR:
1. Open the attached report
2. Locate the table that contains highlight/map
3. Export the data from the table
4. Verify that the data is successfully exported without any exceptions being thrown
